    <section class="services-content-wrapper  pb-10 pb-md-10 pb-sm-10 drive-with-us ">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-5">
                
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 mx-auto  mt-30 mtm-md-0 mtm-sm-0  mtm-300 ">
                    <div class="h-100 bg-white p-3 p-md-4 rounded shadow-sm" style="border-top: 20px solid #a5acb5">
                        <div class=" justify">
                            <h2>Instructions</h2>
                            <h5> Kindly Scroll Down for new Registration</h5>
                            <p>Applicants applying for the First time need to create new account. To start the application for Class 6th, 7th, 8th &amp; 9th admission (Session 2021) in Cadet College Fateh Jang, fill out Details, create your own password &amp; provide valid email address.</p>
                            <p>After registration, an auto-generated confirmation mail will be sent on your Email ID containing the following:</p>
                            <ul class="list-style">
                                <li>Confirmation of Successful Online Registration.</li>
                                <li>Online Application Log-In Username ID.</li>
                                <li>Online Application Log-In Password.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>Kindly save the Username and Password emailed to you for future logins. While applying, you can always save what you have entered and come back later to finish your application by entering Username and password in Log-In area.</p>
                            <h5> Already Registered?</h5>
                            <p>If you have already registered yourself, enter your Username &amp; Password and Click on Log In button available on the Right side of your screen. Username &amp; Password is your email id and passwors is same your created yourself at the time of registeration and is already emailed to you. After Logging-In, Complete your application form where you left off previously.</p>
                            <h5> Documents Upload Requirement</h5>
                            <ul class="list-style">
                                <li>Upload Portrait Passpost Size Picture of Applicant. The photograph must be a recent passport size color picture, preferably in white background. Photographs with Caps, hats and dark glasses are not acceptable.</li>
                                <li>Upload picture of CNIC NADRA ID Card of Parent OR Guardian (Front &amp; Back Side).</li>
                                <li>Upload picture of Student NADRA Form B</li>
                                <li>Pay &amp; Upload 1500 PKR non-refundable application Fee Bank Challan / Voucher. ( Fee Voucher can be downloaded in your online profile under section "Fee Payment" )</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

